{"tid":2180992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人去咗紀念75年前嘅烈士","createTime":"2020-08-30T09:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T09:30:44.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21ce8f82bd1c9ec8d37dede1800a37496a4efb40","tid":2180992,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"【8.30 重光紀念日】<br />\n<br />\n有市民自發到和平紀念碑，進行悼念，並送上鮮花。<br />\n<br />\n重光紀念品，是港英政府當年訂下來的，是紀念香港在二戰後得以重光，亦紀念在「香港保衛戰」中陣亡的將士。<br />\n<br />\n今年因疫情關係，大會堂的紀念花園仍未開放。<br />\n<br />\n攝 / Kevin Cheng @ USP 社媒特約<br />\n<br />\n#USP #USP20200830 #重光紀念日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press/12325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUSP_United_Social_Press%2F12325&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=ee8e53c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press/12325</a>"},{"pid":"ecfdc1ff36cd4d0d83e9d7a5cf464a29d43d9ae8","tid":2180992,"uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSt2s6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSt2s6v.jpg&h=db98624c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Njih1rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjih1rw.jpg&h=4b2d11e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/To8JWZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTo8JWZR.jpg&h=cfef5cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRPQBZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRPQBZS.jpg&h=6ba642c5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}